org.opends.server.backends.jeb.importLDIF

Class Importer.IndexKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opends.server.backends.jeb.importLDIF.Importer.IndexKey
  • Enclosing class:
    Importer

    public class Importer.IndexKey
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used as an index key for hash maps that need to process multiple suffix index elements into a single queue and/or maps based on both attribute type and index type (ie., cn.equality, sn.equality,...).
